<item>
            <title>[LU-17568] Record full path with RMDIR changelogs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17568</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using the changelogs to monitor changes to a file system, deleting directories can result in it being difficult to figure out what was deleted, as using the fid2path utility does not work with fids that reference deleted directories. Recording the full path in the changelogs would allow this information to remain accessible.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="81000">LU-17568</key>
            <summary>Record full path with RMDIR changelogs</summary>
